abstract: The software maker is showing the effects of the troubled economy and the stronger dollar as it reported a 1 percent drop in net income.
snippet: The software maker is showing the effects of the troubled economy and the stronger dollar as it reported a 1 percent drop in net income.
lead_paragraph: The strengthening dollar did more to weaken Oracle’s second-quarter earnings than did the slowdown in the world economy.

headline.main: Despite a Flat Quarter, Oracle Meets Expectations
headline.print_headline: Despite a Flat Quarter, Oracle Meets Expectations
